      <h4>What is a Grocery Optimizer?</h4>
      <p>A simple tool to help you get your shopping done pronto so you can spend more time doing whatever you enjoy.  If you really enjoy taking a long time grocery shopping, this probably isn't for you.</p>
    </div>
	</div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="help">
      <h4>How do I create a list?</h4>
      <p>In between grocery trips, keep adding items to "The List".  You can either add items from "The List" or from "All Items" which keeps all of the items from every trip.  </p>
    

  </div>
  </div>
  </div>
