      <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="help">
      <h4>How do I optimize my shopping?</h4>
      <p>Using the location, go from either left to right or right to left in the store, and indicate where, in general, the item is by using 1 for the very right side of the store and 5 for the total opposite of the store.</p>
    
    </div>
  </div>
        <div class="col-md-6"> 
      <div class="help">
      <h4>How long is this info stored?</h4>
      <p>The list is stored in your browser, but don't worry, deleting cookies won't get rid of it.  The benefit of this vs. storing it on the interwebs is even in the back of the grocery store where you might not get a cell signal, you can keep using your list to tick off what you've bought.</p>
    
    </div>
  </div>


